{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ebe7a20a76","title":"望刘金轩部向汉中方面行动切断胡宗南逃路","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8fd65325f8","index":0,"year":1949,"month":5,"day":8,"articleId":"ebe7a20a76"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji26","name":"毛泽东全集第26卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji26.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji26":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"8e3946976e","type":"paragraph","text":"望刘金轩部向汉中方面行动","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"f04c5fde21","type":"paragraph","text":"切断胡宗南逃路","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"ec38631265","type":"paragraph","text":"1949年5月8日中原局，并告彭、张、赵，西北局（一）我第一野战军（三十五万人）六月间开始举行夺取渣关，西安、宝鸡、汉中、天水及陇南地区之战役，希望我陕南刘金轩部沿汉水尚汉中方面行动，最好能直取汉中区域，切断胡宗南向川北的迷路。（二）在上述战役期间及战役结束后一个时期内，刘金轩（三）在上述战役完毕之后，西安等处之敌已被开灭或驱逐，陕南、读北之联系已经打通，陕南区党政军领导关系应子政变为受西北局、西北政府及西北军区的领导，此种改变之时间大约在七月或八月。在开灭胡宗南的战役中，陕南区应起配合作用。（四）刘金轩部的现状、位置及向汉中进取有何困难条件及顺利条件，请你们迅子查明，电告我们及彭张赵。（五）此电请转发刘金轩及陕南区党委。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"27079a0895","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"6796b083d8","type":"paragraph","text":"辰齐]22","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"cd2041e5c0","type":"paragraph","text":"编通色有品示一尔的有抄博址","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"b60295b780","type":"paragraph","text":"学数中F您第F","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"75aed6373a","type":"paragraph","text":"A在M0270","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"753f672baa","type":"paragraph","text":"A接商N021财社义","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"771b0e5cbb","type":"paragraph","text":"事代镇，可个学代商以年的地）第（A）oo华的有网演到两金数准十关水风所A营我民刘全有部法强水司洋十方面D代起景红的鱼乳域如相办出视验。","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"8426bd5dbf","type":"paragraph","text":"东西店上古料装期的及实得线德一个时入外金杯料受数道精坪新之公金轩自数丝解险三怎受就且塑中气（才达我技完学之传项生你饭","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"},{"id":"c4efa243c9","type":"paragraph","text":"2段）毛泽东致彭德怀、张宗逊、赵寿山等电的手稿（部分]。","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76"}],"page":{"id":"4c9833d7fa","publicationId":"maoquanji26","articleId":"ebe7a20a76","start":388,"end":389}}}},"__N_SSG":true}